Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:46.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:104208,106002}{\i1}A fake warning letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:47.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106002,107462}{\i1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:49.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:107462,109839}{\i1}Wasn't it St. Tail\Nwho stole the swan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:53.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:109839,113551}{\i1}That means the one\NI caught was the real St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:58.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:117096,118890}{\i1}Great! My hands\Nare getting numb!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:09.02,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:127023,129025}Sakuraoka
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:19.57,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:135239,139577}The Mayor's Ambition!\NStealing a Swan (Part 2).
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:35.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152840,155510}Asuka Jr.! You're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:47.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163142,167522}I'm sorry. I not only let St. Tail get away,\Nbut the swan was stolen, too…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:51.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167522,171192}I heard all of the security guards\Nwere given knockout drops.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:52.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171192,172360}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:54.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172360,174028}Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:59.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174028,179617}I'm wondering if you are really serious\Nabout catching St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:02.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179617,182370}Someone mentioned that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:09.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186874,189043}No way! I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:16.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189043,196801}Either way, if the swan doesn't come back,\NI have no choice but to resign as mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:20.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196801,200888}Naturally, your assignment to catch\NSt. Tail will be terminated, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:23.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202390,203891}{\i1}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:25.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204183,205435}Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:35.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212275,215862}{\i1}Then who is going to catch her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:38.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216404,218156}{\i1}Someone else…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:39.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218156,219741}{\i1}Someone else and not me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:41.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220658,221826}{\i1}I couldn't stand that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:43.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222118,223786}Please wait, Mr. Mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:50.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228833,230001}"Tomorrow night
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230001,231377}I'm going to the Okajima residence
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:52.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231377,232420}the mayor of Sakuraoka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:54.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232420,234297}in order to pick up the Swan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:55.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234297,235882}– St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:57.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236299,237884}{\i1}This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.84,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:237884,239844}Sakuraoka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:04.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240636,244390}{\i1}If Okajima's and that car's\Nlicense plate are the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:06.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244390,246476}this is a real warning note.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:10.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247894,250897}{\i1}What should I do?\NShould I leave it to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:15.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252440,255526}{\i1}What on earth is St. Tail\Ngoing to do with the swan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:17.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255526,257528}{\i1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:27.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265203,267663}That's all right, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:31.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267663,271793}If the swan is returned,\NAsuka Jr. won't be fired, will he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:35.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272502,275213}I don't care about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:38.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275213,278132}I'm thinking about the people\Nwho came for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:44.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279425,284263}Why did you go to the trouble\Nof giving him a warning note?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:48.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285431,288643}Because I promised it,\Nand he was depressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:56.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288643,296609}It seems to me you are looking forward\Nto seeing him as St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:57.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296609,297819}Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:06.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302573,306410}Anyway, the important thing now\Nis to get the swan back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307245,309163}{\i1}She isn't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315503,317255}{\i1}I wanted to see…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:23.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319423,323094}{\i1}The eyes which stare only at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:35.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334063,335565}{\i1}I wanted to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:41.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338568,341070}{\i1}That's why I sent him\Nthe warning notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:57.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354000,357837}{\i1}I'll definitely get the swan back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:59.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357837,359463}{\i1}Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375646,378816}Man! This wall is awfully high!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:22.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379609,382236}That's why the rich people are…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385239,386949}Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:28.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386949,388492}Have I been spotted?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:43.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399253,403299}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:49.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408137,409305}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:52.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411641,412975}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:57.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414727,417271}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:16.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432620,436290}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:18.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437541,438918}And with Asuka Jr., too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:20.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439752,440962}Seira…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:23.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441963,443422}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:36.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453683,456394}It went better than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:38.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456936,458354}Mr. Okajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:43.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458354,463025}Don't relax until we take\Nthe swan outside tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:45.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464151,465111}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472159,474370}{\i1}They must be Okajima and Yabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:56.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474370,476163}{\i1}I wonder where the swan is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:07:59.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478207,479000}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:00.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479000,480543}Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:03.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481002,483921}This guy was trying to sneak in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:06.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484797,486424}{\i1}Oh, he really did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:15.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492596,495266}What should we do with him?\NCall the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:18.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496767,498936}The police aren't a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:21.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498936,501814}I have something to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501814,504108}Lock him up somewhere\Nuntil I can give you instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:25.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504734,505526}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:27.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506569,507528}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:28.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507528,508237}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508237,510406}What are you doing?!\NLet me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:32.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511782,512825}{\i1}Asuka Jr.…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516579,518497}How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:40.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518497,520958}Are you, by any chance, St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:46.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521292,526422}If you are, that boy\Nis your friend, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:49.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526422,529925}{\i1}Oh, shoot! I was careless,\Nbecause I was distracted by Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:07.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546734,547902}It's no use…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548903,550863}There's no way out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:18.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555743,558120}{\i1}Why on earth did I come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:20.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558829,560164}{\i1}I'm pitiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:24.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561123,564960}{\i1}I'm the one\Nwho will catch St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:28.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566212,568756}{\i1}No matter what,\NI have to get the swan back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:29.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568756,569840}This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:37.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573761,577765}As you can see,\Nyour friend is safe, Ms. St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:40.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578516,580810}We've been hospitable, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583521,585481}Keep quiet for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:50.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589860,590861}{\i1}It can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:17.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614176,617179}{\i1}I'm sure he can't see my face\Nin this darkness…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:20.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619682,620891}Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:23.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622309,623811}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:25.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623811,625271}{\i1}What shall I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:32.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630526,632403}– Excuse me!\N– Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:37.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633070,637992}Is it true that the warning message\Nin the newspaper was fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:41.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638909,641078}Did that man do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:47.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644081,647710}Please tell me\Nwhat's going on with this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:49.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648586,649712}Otherwise…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:52.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650462,652464}I can't catch you.
Comment: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:02.68,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:662683,662683}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:07.68,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:667688,667688}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:26.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685539,686957}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:30.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686957,690586}So they're taking it\Nout of the country tonight…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:37.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693297,697092}Why are you going to such lengths\Nto get the swan back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:44.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703557,704600}Why are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:12:01.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716612,721283}Oh, shoot! If the case wasn't like this,\NI could have arrested you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:11.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726664,731252}Why don't we cooperate with each other?\NJust this once, until we get the swan back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:15.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734546,735256}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740094,742388}Now that we've decided,\Njust step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:25.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742388,745140}I'll be a decoy,\Nand you can find the swan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:33.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752731,753399}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:35.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754441,755442}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:36.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755943,756944}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759655,761532}Watch out!\NWe're on the second floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:50.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768872,770624}He fell…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771500,773460}I heard something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:54.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773460,774545}What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:55.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774545,775587}Chase her! Don't let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:05.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781927,785597}If she could escape from the room\Nso easily, why didn't she tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:07.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785597,787308}We'll be late\Nfor the boat's departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:10.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788058,790352}Don't worry\Nabout the intruders, Yabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:11.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790352,791854}Bring it quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:18.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:797234,798444}{\i1}Is that the swan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:20.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799445,800696}Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:32.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810456,812333}The back door isn't shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:33.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812333,813667}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:34.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813667,814710}That's strange…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:57.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835397,837733}{\i1}Asuka Jr. got in the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:59.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837733,839568}{\i1}That means the swan is…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:00.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839568,840402}{\i1}I have to chase them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871475,873769}{\i1}Here it is! The swan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:39.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876772,879733}{\i1}But I can't jump out with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:06.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905134,906718}Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:13.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911765,913725}Don't give me any trouble.\NHand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:16.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914059,916478}No! I won't give it to you\Neven if you have to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:04.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961190,964568}God knows all your evil actions!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964568,965903}Return the swan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:09.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967237,969907}Hey! Don't you care\Nabout what happens to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:30.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989051,990385}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:34.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:991970,994181}Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:36.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995682,996725}Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:44.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003857,1004608}My eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:48.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007444,1008654}Grab hold of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:07.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026630,1027631}I won't let go of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:08.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027631,1028382}You…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:11.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030050,1031218}I didn't feel a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:20.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037808,1040143}Let us down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:22.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040143,1042604}Hey! Return the swan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:26.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043146,1046066}Swans fly away in the spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:04.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080517,1084980}You promised me\Nyou wouldn't arrest me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:18.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095866,1098035}But only this once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:20.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098035,1100912}The next time we meet,\NI definitely will!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:25.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101913,1105876}{\i1}You're right.\NI'll see you again…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:57.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132778,1137282}Thank you, Asuka,\Nfor getting the swan back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:58.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137282,1138950}I can't express\Nmy gratitude with words.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138950,1140369}My pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:02.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140369,1142287}But St. Tail is…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:06.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142287,1146792}I now believe you are still\Npassionate about catching her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:13.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147334,1153632}I would appreciate it if you would continue\Nto be in charge of arresting St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:15.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153632,1155801}Really?!\NI'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:25.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163141,1165560}What were you scheming?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:29.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167562,1169022}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:35.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171316,1175487}Rina. Nothing works\Non him right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:39.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177447,1179658}I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:41.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180367,1181368}I know…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:46.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184246,1186998}Because I love him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:48.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186998,1188458}It's all right, it's all right…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:20:00.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196925,1200262}I heard that Mayor Okajima\Nand Yabe were arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:02.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200262,1202097}What happened to that maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:06.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202097,1206226}Mayor Morinaka found\Na new job for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:08.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206226,1208228}Really? I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212691,1214109}Look, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214109,1216445}The Mayor is praising you\Nin the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216445,1218196}That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:29.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227247,1229666}Are you going\Nto chase St. Tail again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:33.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230000,1233420}Of course!\NI will definitely catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:35.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233420,1235130}I won't allow anyone else to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:38.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236214,1238675}{\i1}Hold on!\NCome and catch me!
